text.textPath: Winter Sky over Limbo's Dawn ( ) ~ Tabaxi ~ Haunted ~ Rogue 5 / Monk 2

text.tspan: Artifacts: an obsidian one, and a green marble-y one
Climbing Rope: 60' silk rope holds <= 3K#. Animates on action, moves
<= 10' on BA. Can knot & grant Adv to climbs. 20 AC + 20 HP
Disappear Dust: everything w/i 10' becomes invisible for 2d4 minutes.
Ends if creature makes attack or spell
Healing Potions: Restore HP, Normal (4), Greater (0), Superior (1)
Paper bird - Can send message to B'hood contact if w/i 10d flight
Pyrotechnics Wand: 7 charges, regains 1d6+1/day. d20 on 0, 1 --> gone.
Action to create harmless burst of light w/i 60' & heard 300' away
Shield of Faith: one use, grants +2 AC w/concentration
Thieves' Tools*: small file, set of lock picks, sm. mirror on metal handle,
Misc: backpack, BBs, bedroll, bell, candle, crowbar, dragon tooth,
hammer, hooded lantern, mess kit, necklace, oil, pitons, 10d rations,
if Foe has not moved Gain Advantage
if (finesse or range weapon) & (Adv. or Ally w/i 5')
if Foe surprised Critical damage roll 2x *all* dice

tspan.tspan: Unless I've shown myself a threat,
help, & even fight alongside if alone.

text.tspan: Uncanny Dodge for 1/2 damage from visible foe
Opportunity Attack: single melee attack vs foe leaving range
(4d4 dmg & poisoned [1 min]) or 14 CON save 1/2 dmg
Can use on 3 arrows or 1 melee weapon for 3 hits.
Dash, Disengage, Hide, or Punch (after monk attack) -- FREE
Dodge, or Punch twice (after any attack) -- 1 Ki
